      "title": "Tribute to Fred Burkhardt, former IFRA CEO",
      "link": "https://wan-ifra.org/2026/07/tribute-to-fred-burkhardt-former-ifra-ceo/",
      "published": "Mon, 13 Jul 2026 12:00:59 +0000",
      "summary_raw": "<p>The news media industry recently lost one of its pioneers with the passing of Dr. Friedrich W. Burkhardt on 19 June, 2026. He was 97. As Managing Director of IFRA from 1972 to 1994, he guided the association and the international newspaper community through one of the most profound technological transitions in its history.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://wan-ifra.org/2026/07/tribute-to-fred-burkhardt-former-ifra-ceo/\">Tribute to Fred Burkhardt, former IFRA CEO</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://wan-ifra.org\">WAN-IFRA</a>.</p>",
      "source": "WAN-IFRA"
    },
